SUMMARY:Keys in the Park: A Melodic Duel
LOCATION:400 N Franklin St Tampa \, FL 33602 United States
DESCRIPTION:Join us for an unforgettable evening of musical magic at Keys 
 in the Park: A Melodic Duel happening in the heart of Tampas Downtown! Exp
 erience the thrill of dueling pianos as talented musicians go head-to-head
 \, tickling the ivories and playing your favorite songs. Set against the s
 tunning backdrop of our citys vibrant downtown\, this FREE lively event is
  perfect for music lovers of all ages. So grab a blanket\, bring your frie
 nds and family\, and immerse yourself in an evening filled with laughter\,
  creativity\, and the joy of live music. Get ready to tap your feet\, sing
  along\, and create cherished memories at Keys in the Park: A Melodic Duel
 . \n\nPermalink: https://www.tampa.gov/node/188236
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.tampa.gov/node/188236
END:VEVENT
